  "body": "When trying to compile a project that uses OpenZeppelin Contracts you get unexpected Illegal Import errors that prevent you from compiling it.\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce it:\r\n\r\n1. `npm i -D @openzeppelin/contracts` \r\n2. `npm i -D @nomiclabs/buidler`\r\n3. `npx buidler` and create sample proyect\r\n4. Add `import \"@openzeppelin/contracts/ownership/Ownable.sol\";` to `contracts/Greeter.sol`.\r\n5. `npx buidler compile`.\r\n",
